task_prompt:
Return strict JSON only:
{
  "trades": {
    "SYMBOL": {
      "action": "buy" | "sell" | "hold",
      "portfolio_weight": number (0.0 - 1.0)
    }
  }
}

Rules:
- Default to hold.
- Avoid frequent changes; only buy/sell when stance is directional with high confidence.
- No single position > 0.25 unless confidence is very high.

Return strict JSON only:
{
  "smart_orders": [
    {"symbol": string, "side": "buy"|"sell", "qty": number}
  ]
}

Rules:
- Prefer 0 or 1 order.
- Never oversize; use paper cash and constraints.
- If anything is unclear, return {"smart_orders": []}.
